ZH: 1. 他是一个很好心的人，总是愿意帮助别人。
EN: 1. He is a kind-hearted person who is always willing to help others.

ZH: 2. 她今天特别好心，给了我一些额外的帮助。
EN: 2. She was particularly kind-hearted today and gave me some extra help.

ZH: 3. 我们应该对好心的人心存感激。
EN: 3. We should be grateful to kind-hearted people.

ZH: 4. 在这个世界上，好心的人总是受到尊重和爱戴。
EN: 4. In this world, kind-hearted people are always respected and revered.

ZH: 5. 好心的人往往会获得更多的帮助和支持。
EN: 5. Kind-hearted people often receive more help and support.

ZH: 6. 她的好心行为感动了许多人。
EN: 6. Her kind-hearted actions have touched many people.

ZH: 7. 他们家人都说他是一个好心肠的人。
EN: 7. His family all say he is a kind-hearted person.

ZH: 8. 遇到困难时，总会有好心人伸出援手。
EN: 8. When facing difficulties, there will always be kind-hearted people lending a hand.

ZH: 9. 我很感激你的好心帮助。
EN: 9. I am very grateful for your kind-hearted help.

ZH: 10. 他的好心举动让我记忆犹新。
EN: 10. His kind-hearted gesture remains fresh in my memory.

ZH: 11. 他总是对别人很好心，却不求任何回报。
EN: 11. He is always kind-hearted towards others without seeking anything in return.

ZH: 12. 她的好心举动给了我很大的启发。
EN: 12. Her kind-hearted action has inspired me greatly.

ZH: 13. 遇到危险时，总会有好心人挺身而出。
EN: 13. When facing danger, there will always be kind-hearted people stepping forward.

ZH: 14. 他的好心行为让我更加相信人性的美好。
EN: 14. His kind-hearted actions make me believe more in the goodness of human nature.

ZH: 15. 好心的人往往会把别人的利益放在第一位。
EN: 15. Kind-hearted people often put others' interests first.

ZH: 16. 他的好心举动给了我力量面对困难。
EN: 16. His kind-hearted gesture gives me strength to face difficulties.

ZH: 17. 今天遇到了很多好心的人，让我心情愉快。
EN: 17. Today I met many kind-hearted people that made me happy.

ZH: 18. 街上总是能遇到一些好心的路人帮忙指路。
EN: 18. There are always kind-hearted passersby on the street willing to help with directions.

ZH: 19. 我们应该向好心的人学习如何对待他人。
EN: 19. We should learn from kind-hearted people on how to treat others.

ZH: 20. 她的好心帮助让我感到无比感激。
EN: 20. Her kind-hearted help makes me extremely grateful.
